{"tid":527490,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"邊到可以買到好食,性價比高既cake","createTime":"2018-01-12T16:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T17:49:12.000Z","uid":79081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eeb21cb582b587508dd53ef76c5b2afe420583b7","tid":527490,"uid":79081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:55:15.000Z","msg":"最近有個好鍾意食蛋糕的女同事係做野上邊幫左我好多<br />\n想答謝返佢<br />\n<br />\n香港邊到買到真係好食,唔會太細件,性價比有返咁上下的cake?<br />\n美心聖安娜東海堂不了,我估佢應該食到厭<br />\n價錢唔好太貴,50~60蚊一件都可以接受<br />\n本身想買3件GODIVA,但睇相太細件,我唔係講緊要大大件,但至少唔好50蚊但得一啖既份量。<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲有Cafe/Cake鋪 介紹<br />\n聽日得閒,想聽日內搞掂,質量真係OK既話我去遠少少都無所謂(新界離島唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n碌左半個鐘Openrice都無頭緒,真係走投無路先上黎問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f87f38558d89232af06e5eed92dd09f512c92cf","tid":527490,"uid":79081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T17:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037673bf1b1070a5404afccaa7d7a79d1c619beb","tid":527490,"uid":12879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T17:10:35.000Z","msg":"尖東帝苑酒店 佢嘅拿破崙蛋糕都幾出名 食過唔錯 另外佢有買一件件嘅蛋糕 應該唔太差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50265251236faf5eb570f0e05766f6717cb0268f","tid":527490,"uid":79081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"037673bf1b1070a5404afccaa7d7a79d1c619beb","tid":527490,"uid":12879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T17:10:35.000Z","msg":"尖東帝苑酒店 佢嘅拿破崙蛋糕都幾出名 食過唔錯 另外佢有買一件件嘅蛋糕 應該唔太差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gi